{"tid":198340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"坐飛機你一定遇過嘅事","createTime":"2017-04-12T12:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T12:34:12.000Z","uid":25652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6711904e06c208e90a42b1df72b272b7c63b9db9","tid":198340,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"1. 過安檢個陣前面一定有人要搜身/搜袋<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人影水牌話自己又飛啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 起飛前總會有乘客要人提拉直椅背/收起餐枱/拉起窗葉<br />\n<br />\n4. 飛機入面總會有細路大喊大叫，父母只會「噓噓噓」<br />\n<br />\n5. 廉航有人會買野食/飲，長途機會有人叫杯面<br />\n<br />\n6. 降落時又loop返第3<br />\n<br />\n7. 一降落即刻鬆安全帶/企起身拎行李<br />\n<br />\n8. 返香港時要等好耐先出行李"},{"pid":"afba350ffc1ffe252d4f5a62214be0df4e53a34e","tid":198340,"uid":821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"BB喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4741aa8dc88252a92f442404a2026abf3956c504","tid":198340,"uid":33219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"不停咳又唔掩口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306513fb7eed2a6e7e9c4bb27deaaf6e07d601c5","tid":198340,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BB喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過來回都坐正BB隔離<br />\n仲要全程係咁喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe372318cd92777e3a70690ea6d17a97ab1119b","tid":198340,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"俾隔離位叫熄電話"},{"pid":"09667b221c2ee70afb9c4cc63f0423c9196aad24","tid":198340,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BB喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真細路未有顧及他人嘅意識時就唔好帶埋去旅行啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過有陣時連父母都唔識顧其他人感受，全部人on99咁一齊出醜"},{"pid":"d0a977faff0a23